    {
      "message": "* This NE doesn't use ADmob C++ SDK, only native iOS and Android SDKs\n* Communication Java->Cpp->Lua and ObjC->Cpp->Lua uses unified way through json, for ADS performance for rare events aren't so critical\n* ObjectiveC implementation doesn't use ARC so some objects allocated on SDK side need to be manually managed. Check `SetRewardedAd` in `admob_ios.mm`\n* NE has implementation of some privacy management functions for CCPA ([ios](https://developers.google.com/admob/android/ccpa) and [android](https://developers.google.com/admob/ios/ccpa)) and ATT ([ios](https://developers.google.com/admob/ios/ios14#request)).\n* Instructions how to update NE is available in `DEVELOPMENT.md` file",
